	<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/technet/treeview/default.asp?url=/technet/itsolutions/net/evaluate/FsNETSec.asp">Security in the Microsoft .NET Framework</a>.&nbsp; Coverage of the security tapestry that provides useful concepts and descriptions in appraising any security arrangement.<br>
