	<div class="posts">
	<a name="90094272">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h1>Systems Architecture</h1><h2>Architectural Frameworks</h2><a href="http://www.opengroup.org/architecture/cert/togaf7cert/cert7index.htm">TOGAF 7 Certification</a>.&nbsp; The Open Group Architectural Framework (TOGAF) is at Version 7 and there is now a certification process for it.&nbsp; Certification is applicable to tools, training, architects, and other professional services.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#90094272">Monday, March 03, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
