	<h1>Systems Architecture</h1><h2>Software Engineering and Development</h2><h3>Development methodologies</h3><a href="http://builder.com.com/printerfriendly.jhtml;jsessionid=HMCYQTUMIAG5XTQQABUCFFA?id=u00420021209sob01.htm&rcode=">Builder.com: Large Systems Development -- Points to Consider</a>.&nbsp; More on DSDM, this time in approaching large systems projects.  A 2003-01-28 article by Scott Robinson.<br>
